Sands China Shareholder Selling Stake for $301 Million

-- B y   F o x   H u
-- 
2011-05-31T09:44:34Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-31/sands-china-shareholder-selling-stake-for-301-million-1-.html
A  Sands China Ltd. (1928)  investor is
selling a stake in the company for HK$2.34 billion ($301
million), according to a term sheet obtained by Bloomberg News.  The unidentified shareholder offered 120 million shares at
HK$19.50 each, the terms show. Sands China closed at HK$20.15
today in Hong Kong trading. Credit Suisse Group AG is managing
the sale, according to the document.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Fox Hu in Hong Kong at 
 fhu7@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Philip Lagerkranser at 
 lagerkranser@bloomberg.net  